羅冠聰在中學時期為學校足球隊成員<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1045100a|title=香港輕取新加坡 羅冠聰低調撐場|author=麥馬高|date=2016-10-11|work=[[獨立媒體_inmediahk.net|獨立媒體 inmediahk.net]]|accessdate=|archive-date=2019-11-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191110013127/https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1045100a|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。此外，羅冠聰在中五加入學校辯論隊，因而引起他對時政的興趣<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://theinitium.com/article/20160914-hongkong-nathanlaw/|title=專訪羅冠聰：從雨傘走出的最年輕立法會議員|author1=陳倩兒|author2=張潔平|date=2016-09-14|work=端傳媒|accessdate=2018-10-13|archive-date=2021-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225024314/https://theinitium.com/article/20160914-hongkong-nathanlaw/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 感情生活 ===
他曾與同為活躍[[社運|社運]]的[[袁嘉蔚|袁嘉蔚]]拍拖<ref>{{Cite news|author=莊恭南|url=https://www.hk01.com/article/138640/ |title=兩女將內外分工　眾志公佈周庭戰港島補選　袁嘉蔚任副主席 |date=2017-12-04 |work=香港01 |accessdate=|archive-date=2022-05-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220502131930/https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/138640/%E5%85%A9%E5%A5%B3%E5%B0%87%E5%85%A7%E5%A4%96%E5%88%86%E5%B7%A5-%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%85%AC%E4%BD%88%E5%91%A8%E5%BA%AD%E6%88%B0%E6%B8%AF%E5%B3%B6%E8%A3%9C%E9%81%B8-%E8%A2%81%E5%98%89%E8%94%9A%E4%BB%BB%E5%89%AF%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2019年12月，二人宣佈分手，在社交網帖文中羅明言「雙方真切的感受到性格不合所帶來的傷害」<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/5631679-%E3%80%90kelly-online%E3%80%91%E5%90%8C%E8%A2%81%E5%98%89%E8%94%9A5%E5%B9%B4%E6%83%85%E5%B7%B2%E9%80%9D-%E7%BE%85%E5%86%A0%E8%81%B0%EF%BC%9A%E6%80%A7%E6%A0%BC%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%88%E5%B8%B6%E4%BE%86|title=羅冠聰：性格不合帶來傷害 與袁嘉蔚拍拖5年告一段落|date=2019-12-23|work=巴士的報|accessdate=2019-12-24|archive-date=2020-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201210123309/https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/5631679-%E3%80%90kelly-online%E3%80%91%E5%90%8C%E8%A2%81%E5%98%89%E8%94%9A5%E5%B9%B4%E6%83%85%E5%B7%B2%E9%80%9D-%E7%BE%85%E5%86%A0%E8%81%B0%EF%BC%9A%E6%80%A7%E6%A0%BC%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%88%E5%B8%B6%E4%BE%86|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20191224/s00002/1577124956282/%E3%80%90emily%E3%80%91%E7%BE%85%E5%86%A0%E8%81%B0%E8%A2%81%E5%98%89%E8%94%9A-%E7%B5%90%E6%9D%9F5%E5%B9%B4%E6%83%85|title=【Emily】羅冠聰袁嘉蔚 結束5年情|date=2019-12-24|work=明報|accessdate=2019-12-24|archive-date=2021-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210107193715/https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20191224/s00002/1577124956282/%e3%80%90emily%e3%80%91%e7%be%85%e5%86%a0%e8%81%b0%e8%a2%81%e5%98%89%e8%94%9a-%e7%b5%90%e6%9d%9f5%e5%b9%b4%e6%83%85|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==荣誉==
2016年，獲《外交政策》選為全球百大思想者之一<ref>{{Cite web|title=Global Thinkers 2016|url=https://2016globalthinkers.foreignpolicy.com/2016/profile/nathan-law?3fa4cfa909=|accessdate=2021-01-19|work=2016globalthinkers.foreignpolicy.com|archive-date=2021-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210309035605/https://2016globalthinkers.foreignpolicy.com/2016/profile/nathan-law?3fa4cfa909=|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2016/17年間，三度民意調查選為「十大立法會議員」之一<ref>{{Cite web|title=羅冠聰評分 Rating of Nathan Law|url=https://www.hkupop.hku.hk/chinese/header.html|accessdate=2021-01-19|work=www.hkupop.hku.hk|archive-date=2019-07-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190707033407/https://www.hkupop.hku.hk/chinese/header.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2018年，獲《[[政治顧問國際協會|政治顧問國際協會]]》頒發民主獎章<ref>{{Cite web|title=IAPC {{!}} News|url=https://www.iapc.org/news|accessdate=2021-01-19|work=International Associ|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126143102/https://www.iapc.org/news|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2018年，獲提名競逐《諾貝爾和平奬》<ref>{{Cite news|title=Hong Kong pro-democracy activists nominated for Nobel Peace Prize|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-china-42907587|newspaper=BBC News|date=2018-02-01|accessdate=2021-01-19|language=en-GB|archive-date=2020-02-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200219223328/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-china-42907587|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

美国《[[时代百大人物|时代]]》2020年全球百大最具影响力人物之一<ref>{{Cite web|title=《时代》百大人物罗冠聪、蔡英文、习近平上榜 {{!}} DW {{!}} 23.09.2020|url=https://www.dw.com/zh/%E6%97%B6%E4%BB%A3%E7%99%BE%E5%A4%A7%E4%BA%BA%E7%89%A9%E7%BD%97%E5%86%A0%E8%81%AA%E4%B8%B6%E8%94%A1%E8%8B%B1%E6%96%87%E4%B8%B6%E4%B9%A0%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E4%B8%8A%E6%A6%9C/a-55027451|accessdate=2020-09-24|last=Welle (www.dw.com)|first=Deutsche|work=DW.COM|language=zh-CN|archive-date=2020-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201210123319/https://www.dw.com/zh/%E6%97%B6%E4%BB%A3%E7%99%BE%E5%A4%A7%E4%BA%BA%E7%89%A9%E7%BD%97%E5%86%A0%E8%81%AA%E4%B8%B6%E8%94%A1%E8%8B%B1%E6%96%87%E4%B8%B6%E4%B9%A0%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E4%B8%8A%E6%A6%9C/a-55027451|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2020年，獲頒《馬格尼茨基人權獎》<ref>{{Cite web|title=Nathan Law|url=https://www.magnitskyawards.com/bios/nathan-law/|accessdate=2021-01-19|work=The Magnitsky Human Rights Awards|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225163355/https://www.magnitskyawards.com/bios/nathan-law/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2022年，獲頒華盛頓傑斐遜學院當屆唯一一個榮譽博士學位，以表揚他在爭取人權、民主同自由上的貢獻<ref>{{Cite news|title=羅冠聰赴美獲頒榮譽博士學位 彌補遺憾|url=https://hk.epochtimes.com/news/2022-05-23/82262241|newspaper=大紀元時報 香港|date=2022-05-23|accessdate=2022-05-23}}</ref>。



